name: If I Dont Die Soon, I Will Rule The Demon Realm
author: Hama1GOamMZXO3tEGzERu-o1N
content: Humanity’s strongest warrior was killed by demons amidst a battle and gained the power to reincarnate, but somehow did so as a demon. Only by dying he can go back to living as a human, so he committed suicide non-stop. But things turned out to be the opposite of what he expected…
